data.description: **Please note, due to inclement weather, the open house has been moved to Sunday 2/18 from 1:00-3:00pm** Gorgeous townhome in the highly desirable Summerfield neighborhood is ready for new owners! The charm and allure of this neighborhood is second to none with horse pastures tucked throughout the community and surrounded by farm fields, produce stands and local businesses.  Inside this immaculate  home you will find warm hardwood floors,  granite countertops, high ceilings, a spacious loft, a cozy den which could also be used as a 3rd bedroom and two additional abundant bedrooms, each with a full bath.  In warmer weather enjoy the back deck which is shaded by a pergola and lush landscaping.  This home has been carefully maintained both inside and out, a true find in this real estate market.  Do not delay and schedule your showing today!
